{"parse":{"title":"Group-Occulting Light","pageid":716,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-5-180</b>\n</p><p>Occulting light in which the occultations are combined in groups, each group including the same number of occultations, and in which the groups are repeated at regular intervals.\n</p><p>The intervals of light separating the occultations within each group are of equal duration and this duration is clearly shorter than the duration of the interval of light between two successive groups. (Fig. 42b)\n</p><p>Reference: <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"8d9c307cb7f3c4a32822a51922d1ceaa\">N</span>.<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"d20caec3b48a1eef164cb4ca81ba2587\">L</span>.\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig42.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig42.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"232\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig42.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"8d9c307cb7f3c4a32822a51922d1ceaa\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>North\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>No\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Newton\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Julian date\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"d20caec3b48a1eef164cb4ca81ba2587\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Luminance\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Level (technician training - WWA)\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Latitude (in degrees)\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615221703\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.049 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.056 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 806/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 28